## Import

The Neon project permission can be imported to the terraform state by its identifier which is composed of the project ID,
and the Neon permission ID.

For example, the identifier of the permission with the ID `12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789abc` in the project
`shiny-cell-31746257` is `shiny-cell-31746257/12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789abc`

Import using the [import block](https://developer.hashicorp.com/terraform/language/import):

For example:

```hcl
import {
  to = {{.Name}}.example
  id = "shiny-cell-31746257/12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789abc"
}
```

Import using the command `terraform import`:

```commandline
terraform import {{.Name}}.example "shiny-cell-31746257/12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789abc"
```
